g.text: 1. Parking Lot Can have multiple floors
2. Parking lot should have multiple entry and exit points
3. Parking ticket at entry and pay at exit point
4. Display Message at entry if lot is full
5. Many type of parking slots(compact, large, Disabled,Motorcycle)
6. Parking different type of vehicles.(Car, truck, van, motercycle)
7. Each Parking Floor should should display free slots
9. Admin add parking floor and parking spots
